text:
42-44 New Street-- Sold by 'charles F. Noyes Co. Inc.
for all cash to and investor
represented by Jesse L. Goldberg.

Bought By Investors
Building at 42 and 44 New St. purchased recently by clients of Jesse L. Goldberg through the Charles F. Noyes Co. from the Central Hanover Bank and Trust Co.

Date: Jul 31, 1942

Photo by WM. Henry
